Purchases Filters

Here are some examples of common purchases use cases.

Delayed Product Sales Orders

This filter finds individuals who made a purchase and have an order status of delayed.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Sales Order Status | Is Equal To | Delayed

Find Combined Purchases and Order Number

This filter looks for individuals who made purchases with a combined total greater than $1,000, their order numbers contained MARCH, and they self-identified their phone's contact point as based in New York City.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Order Number | Contains | MARCH
AND
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 1000

AND

Contact Point Phone | Count | At Least | 1
City Name | Is Equal To | New York City

Combined Purchases and Order Start Date

This filter finds individuals who made a combined purchase greater than $1,000, have an order start date in March, and a contact point city equal to New York City.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 1000
AND
Order Start Date | Month Of Year | March

AND

Contact Point Phone | Count | At Least | 1
City Name | Is Equal To | New York City

Gender, Sales Order, and Location

This filter finds males who spent more than $300 and have a location of New York or Boston.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Sum | Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 300
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 300

AND

Contact Point Phone | Count | At Least | 1
City Name | Is In | New York, Boston

AND

Gender | Is Equal To | Male

ALTERNATIVE EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Sum | Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 300
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 300

AND

Contact Point Phone | Count | At Least | 1
City Name | Is In | New York
OR
City Name | Is Equal To | Boston

AND

Gender | Is Equal To | Male
Order Number, Sales Store, and Subject Line Engagement in the Last 3 Days

This filter looks for customers who made a purchase in store number 1283, their order number contained 2020, and they clicked or opened an email with a subject line of NYC In Store Factory Refurbished Sale.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Sales Store | Begins With | 1283
AND
Order Number | Contains | 2020
AND
Order Start Date | Last Number Of Days | 3

AND

Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Engagement Channel Action | Is In | Click, Open
AND
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | NYC In Store Factory Refurbished Sales
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number Of Days | 3

Purchases in the Last 30 Days by Gender

This filter finds individuals who aren’t male and made an order start date within the last 30 days.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Order Start Date | Last Number Of Days | 30

AND

Gender | Is Not Equal To | Male

Previous Purchase but Not in the Last 30 Days by Gender

This filter finds individuals who aren’t male and made a purchase more than 90 days ago but not in the last 30 days.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order | Count | Is Equal To | 0
Order Start Date | Last Number Of Days | 30

AND

Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Order Start Date | Greater Than Number Of Days | 90

AND

Gender | Is Not Equal To | Male
Purchase a Product in the Last 30 Days

This filter looks for customers who purchased at least two non-black hiking boots in the same order in the last 30 days.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order Product | Count | At least | 2
Product Name | Is Equal to | Hiking Boots
AND
Product Description | Is Not Equal To | Black
AND
Order Start Date | Last Number of Days | 30
Purchased a Product by Month

This filter looks for customers who purchased hiking boots or tents in May.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order Product | Count | At least | 1
Product Name | Is In | Hiking Boots, Tents
AND
Order Start Date | Month Of Year | May
Purchased a Product but Not Another Product

This filter looks for customers who purchased kayaks but no safety vests within a certain time frame.

EXAMPLE
Sales Order Product | Count | At least l 1
Product Name | Is Equal to | Kayaks
AND
Order Start Date | Is Between | 2020-05-01 AND 2020-06-01

AND

Sales Order Product | Count | Is equal | 0
Product Name | Is Not Equal To | Safety Vests
AND
Order Start Date | Is Between | 2020-05-01 AND 2020-06-01
